    "A rigorous AI orientation puts AI with a specific purpose on an organization's strategic agenda, while a successful HRrelated AI implementation ability, for example, given by available competent AI developers and project managers, is critical to the execution of such a strategic agenda.",
    "Accordingly, we formulate our first research question (RQ1): How does a firm's TMT AI literacy affect its AI orientation and HR-related AI implementation ability?",
    "Moreover, it is crucial to note that TMTs do not act in a vacuum.",
    "When Hambrick (2007) revisited his originally proposed UET, he noted that the relationship between executives' characteristics and how firms behave could be significantly impacted (i.e., moderated) by different factors, such as the firm's type.",
    "Firm type can be seen as a common configuration of organizational resources."
